      public java.util.Map<java.lang.String,​NamedBufferedImage[]> getCategorizedImages​(java.lang.String imageDirPath)
      Description copied from class: ImageLoader
      Returns map of categorized images under given path.

      Categorized directory structure should be as follows: for each category a directory is present. Directly under category directory image files for that category are present.
